==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Accloy
<hw>Ac*cloy"</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧k*kloi")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>encloyer</ets>, <ets>encloer</ets>, F. <ets>enclouer</ets>, to
drive in a nail, fr. L. <ets>in</ets> + <ets>clavus</ets> nail.]</ety>
<def>To fill to satiety; to stuff full; to clog; to overload; to burden.
See <er>Cloy</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

